title: Track Opens Outdoor Season At Georgia Tech - University of Georgia Athletics - Georgia Bulldogs
content: Track Opens Outdoor Season At Georgia Tech - University of Georgia Athletics  Georgia Bulldogs
description: Fresh off the men finishing in the top 10 for the fifth straight season at the 2022 NCAA Indoor Championships last weekend, the Bulldog track and field teams return to work in their outdoor opener on Friday and Saturday at the Yellow Jacket Invitational in Atlanta.
